{"id":313925,"type":6,"name":"霹雳刀锋","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/09/df/313925_eKk4O.jpg","summary":"四无诡酒，白莲强渡南海。九耀芙蓉，天外恩怨难解。\r\n傲刀天下，青麟雨泣风啸。再战中原，豪杰板荡惊骇。\r\n《霹雳刀锋》讲述了冥界天岳既破，平风造雨四无君偃旗息鼓，在此时却传出，净琉璃为保全一页书，被带往不在四境之内的天外南海，清香白莲素还真决心强渡天海；傲刀天下之内，情势险恶，傲刀玄龙、傲刀苍雷以及傲刀青麟三位城主之间，恩怨情仇纠缠，暗处又有鬼面具虎视眈眈，同一时间九耀芙蓉石出生，引起各方争夺，而芙蓉石又关系一页书的性命，权势、阴谋、斗争孕育而生，素还真、乱世狂刀、洛子商要如何应对如此诡局的情势。","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>霹雳刀锋</li><li><span>集数: </span>30</li><li><span>开始: </span>2003年1月</li><li><span>类型: </span>霹雳布袋戏</li><li><span>国家/地区: </span>台湾</li><li><span>语言: </span>闽南语</li><li><span>每集长: </span>70分钟</li><li><span>台湾名称: </span>霹靂刀鋒</li><li><span>官方网站: </span>http://www.pili.com.tw/</li>","collection":{"collect":1},"eps":[{"id":973988,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/973988","type":0,"sort":1,"name":"刀鋒","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":973989,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/973989","type":0,"sort":2,"name":"九耀芙蓉","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":973990,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/973990","type":0,"sort":3,"name":"蕭瑟風雨","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":973991,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/973991","type":0,"sort":4,"name":"風雲變","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":973992,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/973992","type":0,"sort":5,"name":"四無贈詭酒，還真渡天海","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":973993,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/973993","type":0,"sort":6,"name":"情仇兩難一孤臣","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":973994,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/973994","type":0,"sort":7,"name":"淒雨迷途","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":973995,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/973995","type":0,"sort":8,"name":"悲慟的手足","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":973996,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/973996","typ